Package: reversecheck
Title: Systematically Run R Checks Against Reverse Dependencies
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person(
        "S", "M", ,
        "s.m@example.com", 
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID")
      ),
      person(
        "Doug", "Kelkhoff", , 
        "doug.kelkhoff@gmail.com", 
        role = c("aut"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-7845-4061")
      )
    )
Description: 
    Run R checks against old and new versions of a package to systematically
    test for any breaking changes imparted on packages which take said package
    as a dependency (reverse dependencies). Checks are run in parallel with
    strategies to minimize dependency installation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
